headline: Therabody Brings Science-Backed Wellness to Ulta Beauty --The Nation's Largest Beauty Retailer
summary: Therabody, the leader in science-backed wellness and beauty technology, is proud to announce its launch at Ulta Beauty, the nation's largest beauty retailer. Starting today, a curated collection of Therabody's top wellness and beauty products will debut within The Wellness Shop on Ulta.com and in over 300 Ulta Beauty stores this Fall, bringing innovative and results-driven self-care tools to even more guests.
